# Health Data RAG — the demo needs NO server-side environment variables.
#
# - The example questions are answered from pre-written (canned) responses, so
#   the app works with zero configuration.
# - To ask live questions, visitors enter their own OpenAI or Anthropic API key
#   in the UI; the key is stored only in their browser and sent per request.
#
# Deploy to Vercel as-is — no env vars to set.
